  "prompt": "Will the celebrities who promised to move if Trump won, really leave the US?",
  "response": "The promise made by some celebrities to leave the U.S. if Donald Trump won the presidency was often made in a moment of frustration or political commentary rather than a serious commitment. In practice, very few actually followed through on their threats to move abroad. Most people, including celebrities, tend to remain in their home country for various personal, professional, and logistical reasons. Ultimately, while such statements can generate attention and debate, they often do not translate into actual moves.",
